Muchidzidzo che[[Kupimanzvimbo]], [[gonyanhatu tsazakose]] (equilateral triangle) igonyanhatu rine mativi ose akaenza uye gonya nhatu dzose dzakaenzana. Makonya ari mukati megonyanahatu tsazakose ane [[chidzudzani]], imwe neimwe ine 60<sup>o</sup>.

